repository-code: "https://github.com/hiroki-tamba-research/GenAI-Evidence-Workbench"
url: "https://github.com/hiroki-tamba-research/GenAI-Evidence-Workbench"
abstract: >-
  Public capability and evidence-boundary release for a local-first methodology
  that audits large exported LLM interaction datasets. Raw exports, sensitive
  content, proprietary detection logic, thresholds, and production adapters are
  intentionally excluded.
keywords:
  - LLM forensics
  - AI governance
  - evidence engineering
  - reproducibility
  - data provenance
  - safe-stop
